from dataclasses import dataclass

@dataclass
class Triple:
    subject: str
    predicate: str
    object: str

# EVOLVE-BLOCK-START

def predict(triples: list[Triple]) -> str:
    sentence = ""
    subject = ""
    for triple in triples:
        if not subject:
            subject = triple.subject
            sentence += f"{subject} "
        else:
            if sentence:
                sentence += " and "
            else:
                sentence += " "

        predicate_map = {
            "numberOfMembers": lambda obj: f"has {obj} members",
            "season": lambda obj: f"competed in the {obj} season",
            "league": lambda obj: f"plays in the {obj} league",
            "manager": lambda obj: f"is managed by {obj}",
            "ground": lambda obj: f"plays at {obj}",
            "fullName": lambda obj: f"is formally known as {obj}",
            "chairman": lambda obj: f"has {obj} as chairman",
            "location": lambda obj: f"is located in {obj}",
            "owner": lambda obj: f"is owned by {obj}",
            "nickname": lambda obj: f"is also known as {obj}",
            "chairmanTitle": lambda obj: f"has a chairman titled as {obj}",
            "isPartOf": lambda obj: f"is part of {obj}",
            "leader": lambda obj: f"is led by {obj}",
            "part": lambda obj: f"is a part of {obj}",
            "mayor": lambda obj: f"has {obj} as mayor",
            "champions": lambda obj: f"has {obj} as champions",
            "country": lambda obj: f"is in {obj}",
            "club": lambda obj: f"plays for {obj}",
            "capital": lambda obj: f", the capital is {obj}",
            "currency": lambda obj: f"uses {obj} as currency",
            "demonym": lambda obj: f"is known for its {obj}",
            "language": lambda obj: f"speaks {obj}",
            "leaderParty": lambda obj: f"is led by the {obj} party",
            "officialLanguage": lambda obj: f"has {obj} as its official language",
            "birthPlace": lambda obj: f"was born in {obj}",
            "youthclub": lambda obj: f"came from the youth club {obj}",
            "operator": lambda obj: f"is operated by {obj}",
            "tenant": lambda obj: f"has {obj} as tenant",
            "city": lambda obj: f"is in the city of {obj}",
            "state": lambda obj: f"is in the state of {obj}",
        }

        sentence_fragment = predicate_map.get(triple.predicate, lambda obj: f"with {triple.predicate} being {obj}")(triple.object)
        sentence += sentence_fragment

    return sentence.rstrip(". ") + "."

# EVOLVE-BLOCK-END
